: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Colin Newcomer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40297:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-16-free-wordpress-live-chat-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image.jpeg\" width=\"999\" height=\"667\" title=\"The Top 16 Free WordPress Live Chat Plugins\" alt=\"The Top 16 Free WordPress Live Chat Plugins\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Businesses grow when they find reliable ways to provide an excellent <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/what-is-customer-experience\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customer experience</a> and gain more qualified leads, conversions, and sales.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In 2021, using a live chat service on your website is a quick way to boost your <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/growth-strategy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">business growth</a>, as <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://econsultancy.com/consumers-prefer-live-chat-for-customer-service-stats/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">79% of customers</a> favor live chat over other support channels.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know that <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://www.emarketer.com/Article/How-Helpful-Live-Chat/1007235\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">38% of customers</a> are more likely to purchase from businesses with <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/customers-want-live-chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">live chat</a> support systems?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, it can be nerve-racking to choose the best option for your website from several free WordPress live chat plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep reading to learn:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Why your business can benefit from having live chat support on your website</li><li>The 16 best free WordPress live chat plugins to choose from</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Benefits of Adding a Live Chat Option to Your WordPress Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Live chat solutions have several advantages for your business.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding a WordPress (WP) live chat support plugin to your website will empower you to:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Provide an Excellent Customer Experience</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When customers visit your website, they want quick help and guidance.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.pwc.com/us/en/services/consulting/library/consumer-intelligence-series/future-of-customer-experience.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PwC</a>, friendly and knowledgeable help are among the most important aspects of customer experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>An efficient way to provide a better customer experience while saving time and answering objections is by adding live chat support to your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The majority of free WordPress live chat plugins allow multiple conversations to improve customer satisfaction.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreso, these plugins enable real-time problem solving, making it easier to deliver solutions to the right customers when they need them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Gain Consumers’ Trust and Loyalty</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/us/products/applications/commerce/atg/cross-channel-commerce-survey-333315.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Oracle</a>, 90% of customers claim live chat gives them confidence because they know they’ll get help in real-time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Essentially, having live chat support on your WordPress website will build <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/customers/3-ways-to-delight-your-customers-to-earn-their-trust\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customers’ trust</a> in your brand. When visitors get a live chat experience on your website, they’re more likely to return and make a purchase.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll earn your website visitors’ trust and gain a competitive edge in your industry through <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/marketing-personalization-examples\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">personalized chats</a>, prompt responses, and the helpful answers you provide.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Boost Website Conversions and Sales</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By guiding website guests through their journey from the time they land on your website, you will help them make quick buying decisions, shortening the <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/speed-up-sales-cycle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sales cycle</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using advanced targeted trigger options will help you reduce the sales abandonment rate and increase conversions and sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.emarketer.com/Article/How-Helpful-Live-Chat/1007235\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Studies</a> have shown that more people buy from companies that provide a live chat experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Live chat also empowers you to create answers to common questions. When you make these preset answers, you’re able to provide <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/proactive-customer-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">proactive support</a>, better engagement, and quick response time, ultimately boosting conversions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With targeted messages and proactive triggers through WordPress live chat plugins, you’ll turn a user from a website visitor to a potential customer to a customer and repeat buyer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Improve Customer Engagement and Acquisition</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Live chat supports boost <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/customer-engagement-guide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">engagement</a> and onboarding of new customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When the website experience is impressive, and agents are always ready to attend to customer needs, it will be easy to keep website visitors engaged until they become paying customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers who already trust your website because of the live chat experience will be confident and convinced to submit their information or make purchases.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Offer Better Customer Support&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://econsultancy.com/consumers-prefer-live-chat-for-customer-service-stats/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">research</a>, most people prefer live chat to email or phone support.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will sell more if you prioritize offering better <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/importance-customer-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customer support</a> through live chat systems rather than just relying on the traditional channels of customer engagement such as emails, phone calls, or direct messages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With less cost, you can get more efficiency. Using live chat support on your website will reduce the cost of hiring support agents, helping you better manage your finances.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With WordPress live chat plugins, you can:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Manage multiple customer queries and chats with the ability to have numerous support agents to make customer management simpler</li><li>Understand and offer quick and effective solutions to the problems website visitors might have, all in real-time</li><li>Attend to visitors offline using AI (artificial intelligence) chatbots</li><li>Handle customer requests over long service hours, including weekends, with minimal disruption and privacy</li><li>Offer support in multiple languages</li><li>Track visitors and initiate conversations</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>16 Best WordPress Chat Plugins</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for the best live chat plugin for your WordPress website to get more leads, increase your website <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/how-to-increase-conversion-rate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">conversions</a> and sales, and provide an outstanding customer experience?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the top 16 free live chat plugins you can choose from for your&nbsp; WordPress website:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. HubSpot All-In-One Marketing</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins\" class=\"wp-image-614683\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/wordpress\" class=\"rank-math-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HubSpot All-in-One Marketing</a> is a free WordPress live chat plugin that helps you coordinate your marketing efforts.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add HubSpot All-in-One Marketing to your website to engage and gather lead information for up to one million website visitors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can then manage these contacts in HubSpot’s CRM (customer relationship management) software. HubSpot offers other helpful tools, such as a popup plugin and a form builder.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>HubSpot All-in-One Marketing includes three different live chat systems you can integrate with your WordPress page to boost customer engagement and generate qualified leads for your business.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of </strong><strong>HubSpot</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Attractive live chat widget</li><li>Three live chat types: support, sales, and automated chatbot (for offline help)</li><li>Real-time messaging</li><li>Email marketing for lead nurturing</li><li><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/service/ticketing-system\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ticketing system</a></li><li>Integration with WordPress pages&nbsp;</li><li>CRM integration</li><li>Built-in analytics and visitor tracking</li><li>Multiple chat agent support</li><li>Available for mobile (IOS, Android)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for:</strong> Businesses that use CRM software and are interested in lead generation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/leadin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download HubSpot All-in-One Marketing</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. LiveChat – WP Live Chat Plugin for WordPress</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins live chat\" class=\"wp-image-614684\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-1.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.livechat.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LiveChat</a> is another free WordPress live chat plugin that empowers fast and proactive communication between businesses and their customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You have to be a LiveChat custo